title: 820-00165 wifi issue
message:
Hello, I have 820-00165 which had slight water damage and was not turning on at all, was changed some corroded resistors and reballed SMC. Now it fully works, but has no wifi and cooler spins on max RPM.

please help, what algorithm should I go throw? Thank you

title: 820-00165 wifi issue
message: Power to Airport present on C3521? SMC_WIFI_PWR_EN checked if power is not there?

title: 820-00165 wifi issue
message: i had similar issue, U3550 wifi switch was shorted to gnd. I had to replace the wifi card too, it was shorted too and that killed U3550, before u replace it measure both sides to gnd if 0 ohm or not
